OL,3,CRob Burrow's father dies following
OL,4,Cyears of campaigning for MND community
OL,6,FThe father of Rob Burrow, a former
OL,7,Frugby player who died from motor
OL,8,Fneurone disease (MND) in 2024, has
OL,9,Fdied following a period of ill health.
OL,11,FRob's former club, Leeds Rhinos,
OL,12,Fconfirmed Geoff Burrow's passing on
OL,13,FMonday, 30 March in a statement,
OL,14,Fdescribing him as a 'tireless
OL,15,Fcampaigner for the MND community'.
OL,17,FAfter Rob's diagnosis in 2019, Geoff,
OL,18,Falong with his family and Rob's former
OL,19,Fteammate Kevin Sinfield, helped raise
OL,20,Fmillions for MND charities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
