OL,3,CRob Burrow's father dies following
OL,4,Cyears of campaigning for MND community
OL,6,FRob Burrow died at the age of 41
OL,7,Ffollowing a four and a half year
OL,8,Fbattle with MND.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the Leeds Rhinos
OL,11,Fsaid: "Leeds-born Geoff was a tireless
OL,12,Fcampaigner for the MND community
OL,13,Ffollowing Rob's diagnosis in December
OL,14,F2019 and continued that work after
OL,15,FRob's passing in June 2024.
OL,17,F"A devoted husband, father and a
OL,18,Fgrandfather, Geoff brought Rob to his
OL,19,Ffirst ever game at Headingley and
OL,20,Fstarted his love of the Rhinos.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1774879866
OL,3,CRob Burrow's father dies following
OL,4,Cyears of campaigning for MND community
OL,6,F"Geoff was always a champion for those
OL,7,Fwho did not have a voice throughout
OL,8,Fhis career as a trade union
OL,9,Frepresentative."
OL,11,FLeeds Hospitals Charity have also
OL,12,Fexpressed condolences adding that
OL,13,FGeoff was "an incredible advocate for
OL,14,Fthose living with MND".
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar in June last
OL,17,Fyear, one year on from Rob's death,
OL,18,FGeoff told ITV Calendar: "We have good
OL,19,Fand bad days, but you have got to keep
OL,20,Fbanging the drum for MND for the other
OL,21,Fpatients, sufferers and families."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
