OL,3,CRob Burrow's father dies following
OL,4,Cyears of campaigning for MND community
OL,6,FVowing to continue campaigning, Geoff
OL,7,Fsupported Leeds Hospitals Charity in
OL,8,Ftheir appeal to build the Rob Burrow
OL,9,FMotor Neurone Disease Centre which
OL,10,Fopened in November last year following
OL,11,Fyears of fundraising.
OL,13,FThe centre in Seacroft, is the first
OL,14,Fpurpose-built centre dedicated
OL,15,Fentirely to MND care, research,
OL,16,Feducation and holistic support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
